			<div class="content" id="post-content-2668122">
									

<p>Thanks very much, Dexanote. I wanted to take a very different approach to the contest, and I was a bit surprised that no-one else got in first.</p>
<p>I also wanted the ending (and indeed many of the other hints throughout the tale) to be left ambiguous. Without the context of the site, there is actually nothing here to confirm the existence of the anomalous - everything is up to the reader to intuit.</p>

