<p>Well done! I’m impressed with this! And because the ending is so ambiguous I kind of like to think they take better care of the V-class than the D-class, giving them basic duties and maybe testing them with objects they are fairly certain won’t cause major harm. This was a really feelsy piece and well worth the +1!</p>

